  "local_port": 33252,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How do you pre-select a seat when booking a flight on Royal Air Maroc?",
  "response": "Pre-selecting a seat on your Royal Air Maroc (RAM) flight can enhance your travel experience by ensuring you have the preferred seating arrangement, whether it's an aisle seat, window seat, or extra legroom. Here's a step-by-step guide on how to pre-select a seat when booking a flight with Royal Air Maroc:\n\n### **1. During Booking on the Royal Air Maroc Website**\n\n**a. Start Your Booking:**\n- Visit the [Royal Air Maroc official website](https://www.royalairmaroc.com/).\n- Enter your flight details (departure and destination cities, travel dates, number of passengers) and click on **\"Search Flights\"** or the equivalent option to begin the booking process.\n\n**b. Select Your Flight:**\n- Browse through the available flight options and choose the one that best fits your schedule and preferences.\n\n**c. Choose Your Fare:**\n- Select the fare type (e.g., Economy, Premium Economy, Business) based on your needs. Some fare types include free seat selection, while others may require an additional fee.\n\n**d. Select Your Seat:**\n- After selecting your fare, you will be prompted to choose your seat. A seating map will appear, showing available seats.\n- Click on your preferred seat to select it. The interface may display additional information about each seat, such as extra legroom or proximity to the lavatories.\n\n**e. Personal Information and Payment:**\n- Proceed to enter passenger details and complete your booking by providing payment information.\n\n**f. Confirmation:**\n- Once the booking is confirmed, you will receive an email with your flight details and seat assignments.\n\n### **2. After Booking Through \"Manage My Booking\"**\n\nIf you've already booked your flight without selecting a seat, you can still choose one by accessing the \"Manage My Booking\" feature.\n\n**a. Visit the Manage Booking Page:**\n- Go to the [Manage Your Booking](https://www.royalairmaroc.com/manage-booking) section on the Royal Air Maroc website.\n\n**b. Enter Your Details:**\n- Input your booking reference (PNR) and last name to retrieve your reservation.\n\n**c. Select Your Seat:**\n- Once your booking details appear, look for the option to select or change your seat.\n- Choose your preferred seat from the available options. Note that some seats may incur an additional fee, especially those with extra legroom or in premium sections.\n\n**d. Confirm Changes:**\n- After selecting your seat, confirm the changes and ensure you receive an updated itinerary or confirmation email.\n\n### **3. Using the Royal Air Maroc Mobile App**\n\nRoyal Air Maroc offers a mobile app that allows you to manage your booking, including seat selection.\n\n**a. Download and Install the App:**\n- Available on both [iOS](https://apps.apple.com/app/royal-air-maroc/id123456789) and [Android](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.royalairmaroc) platforms (ensure you download the official app).\n\n**b. Log In or Retrieve Your Booking:**\n- Open the app and log in using your credentials or retrieve your booking using your PNR and last name.\n\n**c. Select Your Seat:**\n- Navigate to the seat selection option within your booking details.\n- Choose your preferred seat from the interactive seating map.\n\n**d. Confirm and Save:**\n- After selecting, save your changes. You may receive a notification or email confirming your seat selection.\n\n### **4. During Online Check-In**\n\nIf you prefer to select a seat closer to your departure date, you can do so during the online check-in process.\n\n**a. Access Online Check-In:**\n- Visit the [Royal Air Maroc Online Check-In](https://www.royalairmaroc.com/en/plan-my-trip/manage-booking) page.\n\n**b. Enter Booking Details:**\n- Input your booking reference and last name to access your reservation.\n\n**c. Choose Your Seat:**\n- Select an available seat from the seating map. Availability may be limited during check-in, and some seats might not be available for selection at this stage.\n\n**d. Complete Check-In:**\n- Finalize your check-in process. Ensure you have your boarding pass with the selected seat information.\n\n### **5. Contacting Royal Air Maroc Customer Service**\n\nIf you encounter issues or prefer personalized assistance, you can contact Royal Air Maroc\u2019s customer service to help with seat selection.\n\n**a. Find Contact Information:**\n- Visit the [Contact Us](https://www.royalairmaroc.com/en/contact-us) page on the Royal Air Maroc website to find the appropriate phone number or email address for your region.\n\n**b. Provide Booking Details:**\n- When contacting, have your booking reference (PNR), personal identification, and preferred seat information ready.\n\n**c. Confirm Seat Selection:**\n- The customer service representative will assist you in selecting and confirming your seat. Be aware that certain seat selections may involve additional fees.\n\n### **6. Notes on Seat Selection Policies and Fees**\n\n- **Paid Seat Selection:** Royal Air Maroc may charge fees for selecting specific seats, such as those with extra legroom, in premium sections, or early seat selection. It's advisable to review the fare rules and seat selection fees during the booking process.\n  \n- **Frequent Flyer Benefits:** If you are a member of RAM\u2019s loyalty program (Safar Flyer) or have elite status, you may be entitled to complimentary seat selections or priority in seat choice.\n\n- **Limited Availability:** Especially during peak travel times, preferred seats may be limited. It\u2019s recommended to select your seat as early as possible to ensure availability.\n\n### **7. Additional Tips**\n\n- **Check-In Early:** Even if you didn\u2019t select a seat in advance, checking in as early as possible increases the chances of getting your preferred seat during the online check-in process.\n\n- **Boarding Time:** Being aware of your boarding group can help you secure a better seat if you need to select during check-in.\n\n- **Special Requirements:** If you have specific needs (e.g., wheelchair assistance, traveling with infants), inform Royal Air Maroc in advance to ensure suitable seating arrangements.\n\n### **Conclusion**\n\nPre-selecting your seat with Royal Air Maroc is a straightforward process that can be done during booking, after booking via the website or mobile app, during online check-in, or by contacting customer service. Being aware of potential fees and seat availability can help you make the best choice for a comfortable and enjoyable flight experience.\n\nIf you encounter any difficulties or have specific inquiries, it's always best to reach out directly to Royal Air Maroc's customer support for personalized assistance.",
